title: Lets Just Get Married ( Michael Blackson and Trae tha Truth interview)
itunes:title: Lets Just Get Married ( Michael Blackson and Trae tha Truth interview)
description:
Today on the show we had Michael Blackson stop by and gave us Breakfast Club's first proposal, as Blackson proposed to his long time girlfriend in the middle of the interview. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of Day" to our president Joe Biden for his comments about the filibuster and Angela helped some listeners out during Ask Yee. Moreover, we had Trae tha Truth call to speak on his upcoming event Trae Day.
